---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Photography — Jinghao Wen">
<section class="page active" id="photography">
  <div class="sec-eye en">Visual Notes</div><div class="sec-eye zh" style="display:none">视觉笔记</div>
  <h1 class="sec-h1 en">Photography</h1><h1 class="sec-h1 zh" style="display:none">摄影</h1>
  <div class="sec-rule"></div>
  <p class="tarot-intro en">Moments collected along the way — bars, streets, food, and light. A camera is just another way of paying attention.</p>
  <p class="tarot-intro zh" style="display:none">旅途中收集的片刻——酒吧、街道、食物与光线。相机不过是另一种专注的方式。</p>

  <div class="photo-topics">
    <button class="photo-topic-btn on" onclick="filterPhoto(this,'all')"><span class="en">All</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">全部</span></button>
    <button class="photo-topic-btn" onclick="filterPhoto(this,'street')"><span class="en">Street</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">街拍</span></button>
    <button class="photo-topic-btn" onclick="filterPhoto(this,'nature')"><span class="en">Nature</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">自然</span></button>
    <button class="photo-topic-btn" onclick="filterPhoto(this,'food')"><span class="en">Food</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">美食</span></button>
    <button class="photo-topic-btn" onclick="filterPhoto(this,'travel')"><span class="en">Travel</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">旅行</span></button>
    <button class="photo-topic-btn" onclick="filterPhoto(this,'portrait')"><span class="en">Portrait</span><span class="zh" style="display:none">人像</span></button>
  </div>

  <div class="photo-grid" id="photo-grid">

    <div class="photo-cell" data-topic="food">
      <img src="/images/photos/2026/New York Bartending School/1.jpg" alt="Bartending School, New York">
      <p class="photo-caption en">Bartending School, New York · 2026</p>
      <p class="photo-caption zh" style="display:none">调酒师学校，纽约 · 2026</p>
    </div>

